2.4 Compliance & Enforcement Documents

Enforcement records must be retained for 7 years after the decision (RCW
64.38.045(4)(j)). Washington requires written notice of the specific
violation before any fine, an opportunity to be heard, and a previously
established fine schedule. The platform must track the full violation
lifecycle and maintain evidentiary chain-of-custody for all documents.

