2.5 Architectural Review Documents

ARC decision materials must be retained for 7 years (RCW
64.38.045(4)(i)). Under WUCIOA, all ARC committee decisions must be
individually approved by the board. EV charging station applications
have a mandatory 60-day deemed-approval deadline. The system must track
protected modification categories that cannot be prohibited (flags,
solar, EV, heat pumps, pollinators).

